    4. Upstream attribution (this NOTICE, the "Source" and "License
       Status" sections above) MUST be preserved indefinitely regardless
       of how far BPT-NEXT diverges.
    5. If the divergence becomes so large that the origin claim becomes
       misleading, BPT-NEXT will be renamed or re-annotated rather than
